{
  "stem": "22869.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, it didn't help any.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, what can you see from a plane?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That this is a uniform from a guy who's-- who's in Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It didn't make any-- I don't know what they thought about when they saw these jackets flying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was lying underneath there, and the bullets were flying around me-- I mean, by the tenth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said to my friend, Ini, I don't think this is a safe place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Look at these bullets-- they're piercing the wood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're flying down upon our head-- and look at how many we have around us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I says, this is not a safe place to stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, let's run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're going to go away to some other place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said to me, no, I'm staying here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They can never penetrate wood like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you see, you see the bullets flying!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, you can stay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I picked myself up, and I started running through the field.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember it as vividly as today, because I repeated to my daughter several times, if there was ever a guardian angel in my life, he was guarding me from these bullets.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a plane following me and shooting at me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was using the theory that if you lie down on the ground, there is much more substance of you that he can catch.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There is more of you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You're spread about the floor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, it's a false theory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But if I'm standing, they only have the width of my body to shoot me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I kept on running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the bullets were flying around me like somebody pours rice on a bride at a wedding.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
